\title{Estimate the sample-weighted effect as in Gibbons et al. (2018)}
\description{This package estimates the interaction-weighted and
  regression-weighted effects (IWE and RWE respectively) as derived in
  Gibbons, Suarez Serrato, and Urbancic (2018). It also implements specification tests for both estimators and the Wald and score tests for heterogeneous treatment effects.}
\details{
The key functions are \code{EstimateIWE}, \code{EstimateRWE}, \code{SpecTest}, \code{WaldTestIWE}, and \code{ScoreTest}.
}
